>> Breast cancer patients
is a good example.

00:00:11.520 --> 00:00:13.530 align:middle line:84%
The first recommendation,
I would probably

00:00:13.530 --> 00:00:16.050 align:middle line:84%
do a 30-day Gerson
Plus program, just

00:00:16.050 --> 00:00:18.450 align:middle line:84%
to get your body's
nutrition, immune system, up

00:00:18.450 --> 00:00:19.792 align:middle line:90%
and running as best you can.

00:00:19.792 --> 00:00:21.375 align:middle line:84%
If you don't have
time for that, go in

00:00:21.375 --> 00:00:23.080 align:middle line:84%
and have the surgery
done immediately.

00:00:23.080 --> 00:00:27.360 align:middle line:84%
But if you do have the time, do
a 30-day presurgical treatment.

00:00:27.360 --> 00:00:29.835 align:middle line:84%
