about five years ago,

00:00:32.880 --> 00:00:34.680 align:middle line:90%
published this statement.

00:00:34.680 --> 00:00:36.810 align:middle line:84%
There is absolutely
no difference

00:00:36.810 --> 00:00:41.010 align:middle line:84%
in five-year survival rates
between simple lumpectomy,

00:00:41.010 --> 00:00:44.760 align:middle line:84%
simple mastectomy,
radical mastectomy.

00:00:44.760 --> 00:00:47.150 align:middle line:84%
Why are we doing so many
radical mastectomies,

00:00:47.150 --> 00:00:49.200 align:middle line:90%
