even if you have--

00:01:06.510 --> 00:01:10.360 align:middle line:84%
and this isn't just for breast
cancer, any kind of cancer--

00:01:10.360 --> 00:01:16.810 align:middle line:84%
even if you have active
cancer in the lymph nodes,

00:01:16.810 --> 00:01:22.640 align:middle line:84%
my recommendation is do
not remove any lymph nodes.

00:01:22.640 --> 00:01:25.310 align:middle line:84%
