healing and otherwise,

00:01:31.540 --> 00:01:35.050 align:middle line:84%
are always compromised,
especially when

00:01:35.050 --> 00:01:39.610 align:middle line:84%
for the most part
surgery, radiation,

00:01:39.610 --> 00:01:42.340 align:middle line:90%
and chemo are not curative.

00:01:42.340 --> 00:01:44.260 align:middle line:84%
