why destroy yourself,

00:01:54.430 --> 00:01:55.330 align:middle line:90%
why maim yourself?

00:01:55.330 --> 00:01:58.840 align:middle line:90%


00:01:58.840 --> 00:02:04.000 align:middle line:84%
The future in medicine as
I see it is the following.

00:02:04.000 --> 00:02:08.020 align:middle line:84%
If we look at where medicine
was 25 years ago, to where

00:02:08.020 --> 00:02:11.470 align:middle line:84%
it is now, we see major
improvement and major steps

00:02:11.470 --> 00:02:12.640 align:middle line:90%
forward.

00:02:12.640 --> 00:02:14.530 align:middle line:84%
When I first started
almost 30 years ago,

00:02:14.530 --> 00:02:18.190 align:middle line:84%
I figured it would take
probably most of my lifetime

00:02:18.190 --> 00:02:20.770 align:middle line:84%
before we would begin to
see major changes take place

00:02:20.770 --> 00:02:24.910 align:middle line:84%
within the legal
system that would allow

00:02:24.910 --> 00:02:27.820 align:middle line:84%
nutritional medicine
to be part of what

00:02:27.820 --> 00:02:30.790 align:middle line:90%
is used on an everyday basis.

00:02:30.790 --> 00:02:33.970 align:middle line:84%
"Time" magazine had an
article a few years back

00:02:33.970 --> 00:02:37.560 align:middle line:84%
about the revolution in
medicine that's taking place.

00:02:37.560 --> 00:02:41.670 align:middle line:84%
