now in the United States,

00:02:48.980 --> 00:02:51.400 align:middle line:84%
you see a sign go
up at a doctor's

00:02:51.400 --> 00:02:55.340 align:middle line:84%
or chiropractor's office,
alternative medicine down here.

00:02:55.340 --> 00:02:57.340 align:middle line:84%
Well, what do they mean
by alternative medicine?

00:02:57.340 --> 00:03:00.530 align:middle line:84%
Yeah, it's different from what
conventional medicine typically

00:03:00.530 --> 00:03:01.330 align:middle line:90%
is.

00:03:01.330 --> 00:03:05.410 align:middle line:84%
You see more and more
physicians using nutraceuticals,

00:03:05.410 --> 00:03:08.698 align:middle line:90%
using healthier things.

00:03:08.698 --> 00:03:10.240 align:middle line:84%
We're heading in
the right direction.

00:03:10.240 --> 00:03:11.290 align:middle line:90%
Are we there yet?

00:03:11.290 --> 00:03:13.150 align:middle line:90%
No.

00:03:13.150 --> 00:03:16.990 align:middle line:84%
In California, as an
example, where I live,

00:03:16.990 --> 00:03:21.790 align:middle line:84%
it's still a felony to
not suggest and/or use

00:03:21.790 --> 00:03:25.630 align:middle line:84%
chemotherapy, surgery, or
radiation for a cancer patient.

00:03:25.630 --> 00:03:31.600 align:middle line:84%
We have to move away from
this mindset and this control,

00:03:31.600 --> 00:03:35.290 align:middle line:84%
strict control on medicine,
and go to therapies

00:03:35.290 --> 00:03:37.390 align:middle line:90%
that are used around the world.

00:03:37.390 --> 00:03:42.100 align:middle line:84%
In the United States, a lot
of even conventional drugs

00:03:42.100 --> 00:03:45.310 align:middle line:84%
