approaches to heal disease.

00:04:13.770 --> 00:04:18.839 align:middle line:84%
There is a vast
database out there.

00:04:18.839 --> 00:04:23.190 align:middle line:84%
Conventional medicine needs
to start looking at it more.

00:04:23.190 --> 00:04:27.960 align:middle line:84%
Legislators need to
start looking at it more.

00:04:27.960 --> 00:04:30.870 align:middle line:84%
