00:05:30.210 --> 00:05:33.300 align:middle line:90%
And it's been proven to have--

00:05:33.300 --> 00:05:43.050 align:middle line:84%
even in the patient base that
we have of the cancer patients,

00:05:43.050 --> 00:05:45.810 align:middle line:84%
